Wenger on Aubameyang's transfer: &quot;People don&rsquo;t realise how much work is behind these transfers. How much uncertainty, how much energy, how much travelling, how much sleepless nights is behind that &amp; its difficult to combine all that together &amp; to make it all work you know?&quot; #afc<br />
<br />
Wenger: &quot;Its so difficult. I made over 300 transfers in my #Arsenal career but they&rsquo;re always longer now, more detailed, more uncertain &amp; you need more people to work around it&quot;
